missing devpts support for D series Samsung TV`s

for rebuild it is important to change in Makefile : 

#kernel directory
KDIR    := /project/PROJECT_NAME/linux-2.6.30.9/  

#and modify if need kernel version module version in hearder file located  in file 
$KDIR/include/vdlp_version_xxxxxx.h

usage: 
insmod <path to>/mount.ko
insmod /<path to>/devpts.ko
mount -t devpts devpts /dev/pts
insmod /<path to>/pty.ko
ln -s <path to>/busybox /mtd_rwarea/sh
/<path to>/busybox telnetd  -l /mtd_rwarea/sh
